sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh Serving
    participant KS as KServe InferenceService
    participant CE as CloudEventConsumer<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant RE as ConsumerEndpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MR as ModelMesh<br/>PayloadReconciler
    participant KR as KServe<br/>PayloadReconciler
    participant PS as PayloadStorage<br/>(memory/DB)
    participant DS as DataSource<br/>(PVC/MinIO/DB)
    participant Client as API Client
    participant ME as MetricsEndpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant EE as ExplainerEndpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant FM as Fairness/Drift<br/>Metric Engine
    participant XAI as XAI Algorithm<br/>(LIME/SHAP/CF)
    participant GRPC as KServe V2 gRPC<br/>Client
    participant Model as KServe Model<br/>Endpoint
    participant SCHED as PrometheusScheduler<br/>(cron: 5s)
    participant PUB as PrometheusPublisher<br/>(Micrometer)
    participant PROM as Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor

    Note over MM,DS: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Payload Ingestion
    MM->>RE: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP (in-cluster, no auth)
    RE->>MR: Forward partial payload
    MR->>PS: Store input/output half
    Note over MR,PS: Reconcile when both halves<br/>matched by inference ID
    MR->>DS: Persist reconciled Dataframe
    Note over MR: Strips __isvc suffixes,<br/>filters BIAS_IGNORE_PARAM

    Note over KS,DS: Flow 2: KServe CloudEvent Payload Ingestion
    KS->>CE: CloudEvent (Knative)<br/>org.kubeflow.serving.inference.{request,response}<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    CE->>KR: Forward payload
    KR->>PS: Store input/output half
    Note over KR,PS: Reconcile when both halves<br/>matched by inference ID
    KR->>DS: Persist reconciled Dataframe

    Note over Client,PROM: Flow 3: Scheduled Metric Computation → Prometheus
    SCHED->>DS: Load organic dataframe<br/>(batch, every 5s)
    DS-->>SCHED: Inference data
    SCHED->>FM: Compute SPD/DIR/KSTest/<br/>MMD/Meanshift metrics
    FM-->>SCHED: Metric results
    SCHED->>PUB: Publish trustyai_* gauges<br/>(model, request UUID tags)
    PROM->>PUB: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Bearer Token (SA)
    PUB-->>PROM: Prometheus gauge values

    Note over Client,Model: Flow 4: Explainability Computation (on-demand)
    Client->>EE: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP (TLS 4443)
    EE->>DS: Load inference data
    DS-->>EE: Historical data
    EE->>XAI: Initialize LIME/SHAP/CF algorithm
    loop Model perturbations
        XAI->>GRPC: ModelInfer RPC<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 (plaintext, in-cluster)
        GRPC->>Model: V2 Inference Request
        Model-->>GRPC: Prediction
        GRPC-->>XAI: Result
    end
    XAI-->>EE: Explanation result
    EE-->>Client: JSON explanation response

    Note over Client,ME: Flow 5: On-Demand Metric Request
    Client->>ME: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP (TLS 4443)
    ME->>DS: Load inference data
    DS-->>ME: Dataframe
    ME->>FM: Compute SPD metric
    FM-->>ME: Metric value
    ME-->>Client: JSON metric result

    Note over Client,ME: Flow 5b: Schedule Recurring Metric
    Client->>ME: POST /metrics/group/fairness/spd/request<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    ME->>SCHED: Register scheduled metric
    SCHED-->>ME: Confirmation
    ME-->>Client: Request ID + schedule confirmation
